We have a stock trailer hitch on our '72 Bus that bolts up to the
frame where the bumper attaches.  It hides inside the bumper except
for the flange that drops beneath the bumper where the ball is.  I
think the tongue weight listed is 100lbs and the max capacity is 1000.

Dave
